article_text:
Cheyenne, WY (82001)

Today

Clouds early, some clearing late.

Tonight

Evening clouds will give way to clearing overnight. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. Low around 40F. Winds W at 5 to 10 mph.

article_metadata.author: Becky Orr

og.description: CHEYENNE - Starting Saturday, Wyoming residents once again will be able to buy health insurance from an online marketplace.
og.title: Health-care enrollment opens again
